%2C%20inflation%20triple%20and%20then%20halve%2C%20soaring%20fiscal%20deficits%2C%20rampant%20labor%20strikes%20%E2%80%93%20until%20AI%20takes%20all%20of%20our%20jobs%2C%20that%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BConsensus%20long-term%20growth%20expectations%20for%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20earnings%20have%20dropped%20to%20record%20lows%2C%20a%20rather%20powerful%20contrary%20indicator.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EA%20shifting%20global%20landscape%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%20said%20de-globalization%20can%20be%20bearish%20for%20margins%2C%20as%20it%20limits%20opportunities%20for%20cost%2C%20labor%2C%20and%20tax%20arbitrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20US%20corporations%20have%20already%20been%20weaning%20off%20China%20since%202017%2C%20and%20margins%20have%20held%20steady.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-deflation-markets-property-real-estate-housing-beijing-2023-8%5C%22%3EChina's%20reduced%20role%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20trade%20with%20the%20US%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20been%20plugged%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmexico-overtook-china-us-top-trade-partner-supply-chain-economy-2023-8%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMexico%2520has%2520edged%2520out%2520China%2Cfrom%2520the%2520US%2520Census%2520Bureau.%5C%22%3Eimports%20from%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20US%20has%20pushed%20Big%20Tech%20to%20move%20certain%20production%20mechanisms%20back%20to%20American%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20bullish%20for%20some%20stocks%20via%20capex%2C%20jobs%2C%20consumption%2C%20and%20less%20exposure%20to%20slowing%20regions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Bank%20of%20America%20strategists%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20pivoting%20to%20energy%20independence%20also%20looks%20encouraging%20for%20the%20economy.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EInflation%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20up%20in%20the%20air%20whether%20inflation%20will%20stay%20sticky%20or%20fluctuate%2C%20as%20recent%20years%20have%20seen%20stagflation%2C%20hyperinflation%2C%20deflation%2C%20and%20re-inflation%2C%20according%20to%20the%20bank.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrategists%20differentiated%20between%20stocks%20that%20could%20see%20returns%20in%20scenarios%20of%20high%20versus%20low%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20companies%20whose%20performance%20shows%20a%20strong%20positive%20relationship%20with%20BofA's%20inflation%20composite%2C%20names%20in%20commodities%20led%20the%20way%2C%20including%20Freeport-McMoRan%2C%20Mosaic%2C%20and%20Devon%20Energy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20that%20showed%20a%20negative%20relationship%20were%20mostly%20consumer-facing%20names%2C%20including%20Amazon%2C%20Best%20Buy%2C%20O'Reilly%20Automotive%2C%20and%20Clorox.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EThe%20end%20of%20easy%20money%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%20cautioned%20that%20central%20bank%20rate%20hikes%20have%20%26quot%3Broiled%20cost%20of%20capital%20assumptions.%26quot%3B%20Up%20until%20recently%2C%20some%20companies%20have%20over-earned%20on%20cheap%20debt%20and%20free%20money%2C%20while%20others%20have%20under-earned%20amid%20a%20lack%20of%20capital%20in%20certain%20sectors%2C%20strategists%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERising%20borrowing%20costs%20pose%20a%20bearish%20risk%20for%20earnings%20growth%2C%20but%20it%20might%20see%20improvement%20from%20labor%20efficiency%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fartificial-intelligence-work-labor-market-linkedin-economist-ai-technology-markets-2023-10%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20the%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-investors-wall-street-bearish-headwinds-economy-recession-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698581701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653be32696f7540cd067c724%3