se%20-%20I%20have%20lived%20half%20my%20life%20in%20one%20form%20or%20another%20in%20a%20treatment%20centre%20or%20sober%20living%20house.%20Which%20is%20fine%20when%20you%20are%20twenty-four%20years%20old%2C%20less%20fine%20when%20you%20are%20forty-two%20years%20old.%20Now%20I%20was%20forty-nine%2C%20still%20struggling%20to%20get%20this%20monkey%20off%20my%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20title%20of%20the%20book%20sums%20up%20his%20incredible%20highs%20and%20shattering%20lows%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bbig%20terrible%20thing%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20life%3A%20%26quot%3BMy%20addiction%20being%20my%20best%20friend%20and%20my%20punisher%20and%20my%20lover%2C%20all%20in%20one.%20My%20big%20terrible%20thing%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlcoholism%2C%20addiction%20-%20you%20call%20it%20what%20you%20want%2C%20I%20have%20chosen%20to%20call%20it%20a%20Big%20Terrible%20Thing%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20heartbreakingly%20beautiful%20memoir%2C%20he%20also%20recalled%20his%20time%20during%20the%20filming%20of%20'Friends'%20-%20both%20sober%20and%20otherwise%20-%20among%20other%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPerry%20wrote%20his%20addiction%20trajectory%20could%20be%20tracked%20by%20his%20weight%20on%20the%20smash%20hit%20TV%20sitcom%3A%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I'm%20carrying%20weight%2C%20it's%20alcohol%3B%20when%20I'm%20skinny%2C%20it's%20pills.%20When%20I%20have%20a%20goatee%2C%20it's%20lots%20of%20pills.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeason%209%20was%20the%20only%20season%20he%20was%20fully%20sober%20which%20was%20also%20the%20time%20that%20he%20was%20nominated%20for%20an%20Emmy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20wrote%20in%20his%20book%20that%20at%20one%20point%2C%20he%20was%20taking%2055%20Vicodin%20a%20day%2C%20and%20had%20to%20try%20various%20ploys%20in%20order%20to%20get%20them.%20He%20would%20%26quot%3Bfake%20migraines%20or%20other%20pain%2C%20and%20sit%20through%20MRIs%20with%20different%20doctors%26quot%3B.%20On%20Sundays%2C%20he'd%20go%20to%20open%20houses%20and%20search%20the%20medicine%20cabinets%20of%20different%20homes%20for%20any%20pills%20he%20could%20find%2C%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20his%20addiction%20to%20Vicodin%2C%20methadone%2C%20and%20amphetamines%2C%20the%20actor%20attended%206%2C000%20AA%20meetings%2C%20gone%20to%20rehab%2015%20times%2C%20was%20in%20detox%2065%20times%2C%20has%20been%20on%20life%20support%20and%20has%20spent%20between%20%247-%249%20million%20trying%20to%20get%20sober%2C%20Perry%20detailed%20in%20his%20book.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20'Friends'%20cast%20-%20Jennifer%20Aniston%2C%20Courteney%20Cox%2C%20Matt%20LeBlanc%2C%20Lisa%20Kudrow%20and%20David%20Schwimmer%20-%20was%20supportive%20of%20him%20during%20this%20period%2C%20he%20wrote.%20First%20Aniston%2C%20and%20later%2C%20others%20approached%20him%20and%20told%20them%20they%20knew%20what%20was%20going%20on%20with%20him%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20did%20die%2C%20it%20would%20shock%20people%2C%20but%20it%20wouldn't%20surprise%20anybody.%20And%20that's%20a%20very%20scary%20thing%20to%20be%20living%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20his%20book.%20Matthew%20Perry%20was%20found%20dead%20at%20his%20home%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20on%20Saturday.%20He%20was%2054.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698580680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F3spr3vq_matthew-perry_625x300_29_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmatthew-perry-i-should-be-dead-the-one-where-matthew-perry-spoke-about-drug-abuse-4524974%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20should%20be%20dead%2C%26quot%3B%20'actor%20Matthew%20Perry%20wrote%20in%20the%20prologue%20of%20his%20memoir%20'Friends%2C%20Lovers%20and%20the%20Big%20Terrible%20Thing'%2C%20published%20last%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmatthew-perry-i-should-be-dead-the-one-where-matthew-perry-spoke-abo