20a%20business%20coach%20helped%20her%20turn%20things%20around.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Sophia%20Strother%2C%20a%2043-year-old%20founder%20of%20a%20multimillion%20dollar%20delivery%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fl2eindustriesllc.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Ecompany%20called%20L2E%20Industries%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Austin%2C%20Texas.%20The%20revenue%20her%20business%20made%20has%20been%20verified%20by%20Insider.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202018%2C%20I%20was%20reading%20a%20magazine%20and%20I%20saw%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-delivery-service-partners-how-to-apply-2018-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3E%20an%20article%20about%20Amazon%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20company%20was%20being%20ridiculed%20for%20not%20partnering%20with%20small%20businesses%20to%20do%20its%20deliveries.%20The%20article%20said%20that%20for%20%2410%2C000%2C%20anyone%20could%20work%20with%20Amazon%20and%20potentially%20make%20%2474%2C000%20to%20%243%20million%20a%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20a%2038-year-old%20single%20mom%20and%20sex-trafficking%20survivor%20living%20in%20the%20Austin%2C%20Texas%20area.%20My%20grandma%20really%20believed%20in%20me%20and%20she%20helped%20me%20to%20build%20a%20business%20acumen.%20Even%20though%20I%20had%20a%20child%20at%20the%20age%20of%2015%2C%20I%20was%20still%20able%20to%20go%20to%20college%20and%20get%20my%20bachelors%20and%20masters%20in%20business%20administration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%2020%20years%20old%2C%20I%20started%20my%20consulting%20business%2C%20Trustworthy%20Consulting.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20graduated%2C%20I%20owned%20two%20homes%20and%20had%20two%20degrees.%20As%20I%20read%20the%20Amazon%20article%2C%20I%20was%20sitting%20down%20thinking%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Ewait%20a%20minute.%20Why%20not%20me%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20applied%20for%20the%20partnership%20and%20within%20a%20year%2C%20I%20was%20running%20a%20million-dollar%20business.%20After%2018%20months%2C%20my%20delivery%20company%20grew%20to%20become%20a%20multimillion-dollar%20business.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20took%20almost%20a%20year%20to%20process%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flogistics.amazon.com%2Fmarketing%2Fwebinars%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3EAmazon%20Delivery%20Service%20Partner%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20application%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20submitted%20an%20online%20application%2C%20a%20resume%2C%20and%20some%20financial%20documents.%20Then%20Amazon%20ran%20a%20background%20check.%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20transportation%20background%2C%20but%20within%20the%20application%2C%20I%20talked%20about%20initiatives%20I've%20led%20and%20how%20passionate%20I%20was%20for%20serving%20people%20and%20families%20in%20my%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202019%2C%20Amazon%20wanted%20me%20to%20come%20to%20Seattle%2C%20Washington%2C%20to%20interview%20for%20the%20partnership%2C%20but%20I%20had%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20trip%20myself.%20I%20didn't%20have%20the%20money%20or%20a%20babysitter%2C%20and%20with%20only%20one%20week%20to%20accept%20the%20interview%2C%20I%20turned%20it%20down.%20I%20didn't%20believe%20I%20could%20do%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20same%20year%2C%20the%20day%20after%20Christmas%2C%20I%20got%20an%20email%20from%20Amazon%20saying%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20are%20you%20still%20interested%20in%20this%20opportunity%3F%26quot%3B%20This%20time%2C%20I%20knew%20I'd%20regret%20it%20if%20I%20didn't%20let%20things%20play%20out.%20I%20went%20to%20Las%20Vegas%20for%20the%20Amazon%20event%20and%20there%20were%20over%20200%20people%20in%20the%20room.%20Each%20candidate%20had%20to%20be%20interviewed%20by%20an%20Amazon%20executive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20my%20interview%20they%20asked%20a%20critical%20question%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20remember%20the%20interviewer%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BAre%20you%20going%20to%20work%20everyday%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bno%20ma'am.%20I%20believe%20in%20work-life%20balance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20days%20later%2C%20I%20got%20a%20call%20and%20they%20extended%20me%20an%20Amazon%20partnership.%20We%20entered%20a%20formal%20contract%20for%20the%20Austin%2C%20Texas%20area%20in%20July%202020.%20Then%2C%20I%20launched%20my%20first%20route%20for%20my%20company%20on%20September%2022%2C%202020.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20now%20own%20my%20own%20business%20called%20L2E%20Industries%2C%20which%20stands%20for%20Learning%202%20Exhale%20Industries%2C%20and%20Amazon%20is%20my%20transportation%20client.%20We%20just%20cleared%20over%20%243%20million%20in%20less%20than%20three%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20team%20has%20been%20able%20to%20deliver%20over%204%20million%20packages%20and%20complete%20over%2020%2C000%20routes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20now%20have%20a%20fleet%20of%2038%20blue%20vans%20with%20%26quot%3BPrime%26quot%3B%20painted%20on%20the%20side%20and%20my%20company%20has%20grown%20to%20almost%2080%20associates.%20My%20delivery%20team%20goes%20to%20the%20Amazon%20delivery%20stations%2C%20they%20pick%20up%20the%20orders%20that%20customers%20put%20in%2C%20and%20come%20to%20your%20front%20door%20or%20business%20delivering%20the%20packages%20%E2%80%94%20hopefully%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI'm%20responsible%20for%20servicing%20a%20portion%20of%20Central%20Texas.%20We're%20given%2025%20to%2035%20daily%20routes%20and%20I%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20vans%20are%20in%20place%20and%20my%20staff%20is%20dressed%20and%20ready%20to%20go.%20On%20the%20backend%2C%20I%20lead%20the%20operational%20duties%20for%20my%20company%20and%20plan%20ahead%20for%20the%20various%20routes%20my%20associates%20need%20to%20take%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20the%20route%20is%20rural%2C%20urban%2C%20or%20underdeveloped.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20company%20is%20paid%20per%20delivery%20package%20and%20rewarded%20for%20customer%20service%20and%20safety%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20goal%20is%20to%20maximize%20and%20leverage%20safety%20and%20quality%20to%20generate%20revenue.%20We're%20paid%20per%20package%20that's%20delivered%20and%20we're%20rewarded%20for%20being%20safe%20and%20for%20positive%20remarks%20that%20customers%20leave%20us.%20Whenever%20a%20person%20gets%20a%20package%2C%20they%20get%20a%20message%20where%20they%20can%20leave%20a%20remark%20based%20on%20a%20delivery.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Was%20it%20on%20time%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EWere%20the%20delivery%20drivers%20courteous%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EDid%20they%20go%20above%20and%20beyond%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20I%20encourage%20people%20to%20always%20answer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOverall%2C%20we%20are%20incentivized%20financially%20through%20customer%20satisfaction%2C%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20delivery%2C%20and%20for%20consistency%20and%20reliability.%20However%2C%20I%20don't%20directly%20control%20the%20growth%20of%20my%20business%20%E2%80%94%20Amazon%20does.%20It%20dictates%20how%20much%20work%20I%20receive%20based%20on%20overall%20demand%20and%20volume%20of%20packages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20can't%20say%20we're%20going%20to%20average%2040%20routes%20a%20day%20in%202024%2C%20but%20I%20can%20say%20we'll%20use%20a%20certain%20percentage%20from%20our%20proceeds%20to%20form%20other%20conglomerates.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20had%20one%20rough%20quarter%20in%202021%2C%20but%20in%20business%2C%20you%20have%20to%20have%20a%20positive%20attitude%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-gained-employee-trust-boosted-morale-tough-quarter-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3EReinforcing%20a%20positive%20company%20culture%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20helps%20employees%20to%20stick%20it%20out%20when%20times%20get%20rough.%20That's%20what%20happened%20to%20my%20company.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20a%20quarter%20that%20was%20a%20very%20rough%20patch.%20A%20fatal%20winter%20storm%20came%20to%20Texas%20in%20February%202021%20and%20shut%20down%20the%20business%20for%20one%20week.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20succeeding%20quarter%20was%20devastating.%20I%20had%20to%20cash%20out%20my%20retirement%20and%20personal%20savings%2C%20and%20stop%20paying%20myself%20in%20order%20to%20pay%20my%20employees.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEventually%2C%20I%20sat%20down%20with%20a%20temporary%20business%20coach%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Amazon%20provided%20%E2%80%94%20for%2015%20minutes%2C%20and%20she%20broke%20down%20some%20numbers%20for%20me.%20She%20showed%20me%20the%20metrics%20of%20individuals%20that%20were%20negatively%20affecting%20my%20entire%20business.%20From%20that%20point%2C%20I%20had%20to%20learn%20to%20balance%20caring%20about%20people's%20feelings%20and%20caring%20about%20the%20bottom%20line.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20propelled%20me%20to%20refocus%20and%20turn%20my%20company%20around.%20After%20that%20meeting%2C%20I%20gave%20those%20employees%20a%20deadline%20t