re%20would%20be%20time%20to%20ask%20tough%20questions%2C%20including%20of%20himself%2C%20after%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20spokesperson%2C%20asked%20about%20Netanyahu's%20comments%20during%20a%20daily%20briefing%20with%20reporters%2C%20declined%20to%20respond%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20now%20at%20war%2C%20focused%20on%20the%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20officials%20have%20said%20events%20leading%20up%20to%20and%20including%20the%20handling%20of%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20itself%20would%20be%20investigated%2C%20but%20that%20the%20current%20focus%20was%20on%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENetanyahu's%20now-deleted%20post%20had%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BAt%20no%20time%20and%20no%20stage%20was%20a%20warning%20given%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Netanyahu%20regarding%20war%20intentions%20of%20Hamas.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20all%20security%20officials%2C%20including%20the%20head%20of%20army%20intelligence%20and%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Shin%20Bet%2C%20estimated%20that%20Hamas%20was%20deterred%20and%20interested%20in%20an%20arrangement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20second%20post%20on%20X%20about%2010%20hours%20later%2C%20Netanyahu%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20his%20remarks%20%26quot%3Bshould%20not%20have%20been%20made%20and%20I%20apologize%20for%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20give%20full%20backing%20to%20all%20the%20heads%20of%20the%20security%20branches%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENetanyahu's%20initial%20comments%20were%20promptly%20rebuked%20by%20current%20and%20past%20allies%2C%20including%20Benny%20Gantz%2C%20a%20former%20defense%20minister%20who%20is%20now%20in%20Netanyahu's%20war%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGantz%20said%20on%20X%20that%20Netanyahu%20should%20retract%20what%20he%20said%20and%20let%20the%20matter%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20are%20at%20war%2C%20leadership%20must%20show%20responsibility%2C%20decide