india.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fthousands-break-into-un-aid-warehouses-in-gaza-in-a-sign-of-growing-desperation-as-war-escalates%2Famp_articleshow%2F104799988.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fthousands-break-into-un-aid-warehouses-in-gaza-in-a-sign-of-growing-desperation-as-war-escalates%2Famp_articleshow%2F104799988.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAt%20No%20Stage%2C%20Time%26quot%3B%20Warning%20Was%20Given%20To%20Me%20About%20Hamas%20Attack%20%3A%20Israel%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20on%20Sunday%20took%20a%20jab%20at%20his%20intelligence%20chiefs%2C%20saying%20they%20never%20warned%20him%20Hamas%20was%20planning%20its%20wide-scale%20attack%20on%20Oct.%207%20and%20causing%20a%20political%20uproar%20and%20a%20rift%20within%20his%20war%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%2C%20who%20has%20drawn%20public%20ire%20for%20not%20taking%20responsibility%20over%20the%20intelligence%20and%20operational%20failures%20surrounding%20Hamas'%20rampage%20through%20southern%20Israel%2C%20later%20erased%20the%20remarks%20posted%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X%20at%201%20a.m.%20Sunday%20(about%202300%20GMT%20on%20Saturday).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20top%20officials%20-%20from%20the%20heads%20of%20the%20military%20and%20the%20Shin%20Bet%20domestic%20spy%20service%20to%20his%20finance%20minister%20-%20have%20all%20acknowledged%20their%20failures%2C%20Netanyahu%20has%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20only%20said%20that%20there%20would%20be%20time%20to%20ask%20tough%20questions%2C%20including%20of%20himself%2C%20after%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20spokesperson%2C%20asked%20about%20Netanyahu's%20comments%20during%20a%20daily%20briefing%20with%20reporters%2C%20declined%20to%20respond%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20now%20at%20war%2C%20focused%20on%20the%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENetanyahu's%20post%20had%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BAt%20no%20time%20and%20no%20stage%20was%20a%20warning%20given%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Netanyahu%20regarding%20war%20intentions%20of%20Hamas.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20all%20security%20officials%2C%20including%20the%20head%20of%20army%20intelligence%20and%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Shin%20Bet%2C%20estimated%20that%20Hamas%20was%20deterred%20and%20interested%20in%20an%20arrangement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20were%20quickly%20rebuked%20by%20current%20and%20past%20allies%2C%20including%20Benny%20Gantz%2C%20a%20former%20defense%20minister%20who%20is%20now%20in%20Netanyahu's%20war%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGantz%20said%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20that%20Netanyahu%20should%20take%20back%20what%20he%20said%20and%20let%20the%20matter%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20are%20at%20war%2C%20leadership%20must%20show%20responsibility%2C%20decide%20to%20do%20the%20right%20things%20and%20bolster%20the%20forces%20in%20a%20way%20that%20they%20can%20carry%20out%20what%20we%20demand%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Gantz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20spokesperson%2C%20asked%20about%20Netanyahu's%20comments%20during%20a%20daily%20briefing%20with%20reporters%2C%20declined%20to%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20surprise%20Hamas%20attack%20was%20the%20deadliest%20day%20of%20Israel's%2075-year%20history.%20Israel%20has%20since%20bombarded%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20with%20devastating%20air%20strikes%20and%20begun%20ground%20operations%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20toppling%20the%20Iran-backed%20Islamist%20group%20and%20returning%20scores%20of%20captives%20abducted%20from%20Israel%20to%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20saw%20his%20Twitter%20(the%20former%20name%20for%20X)%20from%20overnight%2C%20which%20points%20to%20just%20one%20thing%3A%20he%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20security%2C%20he%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20hostages%2C%20only%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20opposition%20lawmaker%20Avigdor%20Lieberman%2C%20once%20