929%5C%22%3Esome%20trucks%20carrying%20urgently%20needed%20humanitarian%20aid%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0were%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20in%20recent%20days%20from%20Egypt.%20And%20on%20Friday%20evening%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fisrael-hamas-war-netanyahu-warns-of-long-war-ahead-in-gaza%2Flive-67241220%5C%22%3EIsrael%20intensified%20its%20airstrikes%20and%20expanded%20its%20ground%20operations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20sealed%20all%20its%20crossing%20points%20with%20Gaza%20after%20the%20terrorist%20attacks%20by%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhamas%2Ft-19034915%5C%22%3Emilitant%20group%20Hamas%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20October%207%2C%20which%20killed%20more%20than%201%2C400%20Israelis%20in%20the%20southern%20communities%20near%C2%A0the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20At%20least%20229%20people%20were%20taken%20captive%20and%20are%20being%20held%20as%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fonline-video-project-remembers-those-kidnapped-by-hamas%2Fa-67230211%5C%22%3Ehostages%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Israel%20has%20pounded%20Gaza%20with%20air%20and%20artillery%20strikes%20for%20weeks.%C2%A0According%20to%20the%20Gaza%20health%20authorities%20controlled%20by%20Hamas%2C%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20have%20killed%20more%20than%207%2C000%20people%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20is%20classified%20as%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20by%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Germany%20and%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Nonstop%20bombing%20from%20the%20tanks%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMathkour%C2%A0and%20her%20family%20used%20to%20live%20in%20an%20area%20north%20of%20Gaza%20City%2C%20close%20to%20the%20Israeli%20border.%20When%20the%20war%20started%2C%20the%20family%20quickly%20moved%20to%20a%20hotel%20in%20the%20center%20of%20Gaza%20City%2C%20which%20is%20an%20area%20that%20was%20considered%20relatively%20safe%C2%A0in%20previous%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20time%2C%20the%20Israeli%C2%A0military%20told%C2%A0the%20hotels%20they%20had%20to%C2%A0evacuate%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20all%20the%20residents%20of%20Gaza%20City%2C%20with%20the%20military%20telling%20Palestinians%20to%20leave%20their%20homes%20in%20the%20north%20and%20head%20to%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20other%20residents%2C%20Mathkour%C2%A0and%20her%20family%20headed%20to%20the%20southernmost%20city%20of%20Rafah%20and%20stayed%20with%20relatives%20there.%20But%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20any%20safer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLast%20night%20it%20was%20hell.%20It%20was%20the%20worst%20throughout%20all%20nights%20that%20we%E2%80%99ve%20experienced%20since%20we%E2%80%99ve%20come%20to%20Rafah%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mathkour%C2%A0on%20Friday.%20It%20was%20nonstop%20bombing%20from%20the%20tanks%2C%20and%20some%20close%20bombings%20in%20the%20area%20shook%20the%20whole%20house.%20You%20can%20imagine%20how%20terrified%20we%20were.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20part%20of%20Mathkour%20also%20dreads%20the%20difficult%20choice%20she%20will%20have%20to%20make%20if%20the%20border%20crossing%20ever%20opens.%20Only%20those%20with%20dual%20citizenship%20and%20their%20closest%20relatives%20will%20be%20on%20the%20evacuation%20lists%2C%20and%20many%20of%20her%20friends%20and%20neighbours%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20this%20potential%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20bad%20also%20because%20people%20turn%20to%20me%2C%20asking%20me%20questions%2C%20because%20I%20am%20a%20dual%20national%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mathkour.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20what%20about%20the%20others%3F%20Why%20is%20the%20world%20not%20looking%20at%20them%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Our%20focus%2C%20mind%20and%20spirit%20are%20in%20Gaza%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20world%20away%20in%20the%20Old%20City%20in%20Israeli-annexed%20east%20Jerusalem%2C%20Palestinian%20chef%20Izzeldin%20Bukhari%20is%20deeply%20worried%20about%20his%20relatives%20in%20Gaza%2C%20among%20them%20his%20sister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20all%20very%20concerned%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20Gaza.%20Our%20focus%2C%20mind%20and%20spirit%20are%20in%20Gaza%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9C7%20a.m.%20in%20the%20morning%20is%20really%20a%20scary%20time%2C%20because%20we%20are%20waiting%20to%20hear%20from%20my%20family.%20It%E2%80%99s%20very%20consuming%2C%20draining.%20There%20is%20no%20way%20to%20get%20it%20out%20of%20your%20mind.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20his%20mother%E2%80%99s%20family%20lives%20in%20Gaza%2C%20but%20he%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20able%20to%20visit%20them%20for%20more%20than%2016%20years.%20Israel%2C%20and%20partially%20Egypt%2C%20have%20maintained%20a%20tight%20closure%20on%20the%20Hamas-ruled%20territory%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%C2%A0difficult%20for%20Palestinians%20from%20east%20Jerusalem%20or%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Foccupied-west-bank%2Ft-38397942%5C%22%3Eoccupied%20West%20Bank%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20get%20permits%20from%20Israeli%20authorities%20to%20enter%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBukhari%E2%80%99s%20family%20used%20to%20live%20in%20Rimal%2C%20an%20upscale%20neighbourhood%20in%20the%20center%20of%20Gaza%20City%2C%20which%20has%20reportedly%20been%20hit%20hard%20during%20this%20war.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20aunt%20was%20killed%20in%20Rimal%2C%20she%20tried%20to%20evacuate%20three%20times%20but%20there%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20strikes%2C%20so%20they%20had%20to%20come%20back%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bukhari.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20are%20moving%20around%20going%20from%20one%20location%20to%20another%2C%20hoping%20there%20is%20a%20better%20shelter.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20his%20relatives%20moved%20to%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20Strip.%20But%20staying%20in%20touch%20has%20become%20more%20and%20more%20difficult%2C%20as%20co