mesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fpalestinian-red-crescent-says-israel-asks-it-to-immediately-evacuate-al-quds-hospital%2Famp_articleshow%2F104799040.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fpalestinian-red-crescent-says-israel-asks-it-to-immediately-evacuate-al-quds-hospital%2Famp_articleshow%2F104799040.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Massive%20Protests%20In%20Assam%20After%20Landslide%20Hits%20Mega%20Power%20Project%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMassive%20protests%20have%20erupted%20in%20Assam%20after%20a%20massive%20landslide%20hit%20an%20under-construction%20dam%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20on%20Friday%2C%20affecting%20a%202%2C000%20megawatt%20(MW)%20hydroelectric%20project%20and%20reducing%20water%20flow%20in%20Assam's%20Subansiri%20river.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20already%20seen%20the%20adverse%20effect%20of%20dams%20in%20Sikkim%2C%20how%20it%20breached%20and%20so%20many%20people%20died.%20Now%20this%20sudden%20reduction%20of%20water%20in%20Subansiri%20has%20made%20us%20worried%2C%20we%20don't%20sleep%20the%20entire%20night%20since%20we%20live%20beside%20the%20river%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20protesting%20villagers%2C%20Deben%20Dutta%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20protesting%20villager%20Maya%20Nath%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20worried%2C%20suddenly%20there%20might%20be%20a%20huge%20rush%20of%20water%2C%20we%20are%20keeping%20a%20constant%20watch%20on%20the%20river%2C%20we%20are%20not%20sending%20children%20to%20school%2C%20we%20have%20kept%20boats%20prepared%2C%20we%20are%20in%20panic%20mode%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20weeks%20after%20another%20disaster%20hit%20the%20Northeast%20-%20a%20dam%20breach%20in%20Sikkim%20following%20a%20glacial%20lake%20outburst%20caused%20massive%20flash%20floods%20and%20several%20deaths.%20The%20landslide%20has%20alarmed%20the%20authorities%20in%20Assam's%20Lakhimpur%20district%2C%20downstream%20of%20the%20dam%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20dam%20at%20the%202%2C000%20megawatts%20lower%20Subansiri%20Hydropower%20project%20is%20one%20of%20the%20mega%20dams%20being%20developed%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%20The%20landslide%20blocked%20a%20diversion%20tunnel%20in%20the%20Subansiri%20river%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20drastic%20reduction%20in%20the%20downstream%20water%20flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20the%20only%20diversion%20tunnel%20in%20use%20at%20the%20Subansiri%20Lower%20Hydroelectric%20Project%20as%20the%20other%20four%20diversion%20tunnels%20had%20already%20been%20blocked%20earlier%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20National%20Hydroelectric%20Power%20Corporation%2C%20the%20mega%20dam%20developer%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%20We%20accept%20that%20we%20are%20facing%20some%20hurdles%20and%20now%20the%20focus%20is%20to%20close%20the%20gate%20of%20diversion%20tunnels%20so%20that%20landslides%20don't%20affect%20them%26quot%3B%20AN%20Mohammad%2C%20senior%20consultant%2C%20NHPC%2C%20told%20reporters%20at%20the%20dam%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20issued%20an%20advisory%2C%20asking%20people%20to%20restrain%20from%20activities%20like%20fishing%2C%20swimming%2C%20bathing%20and%20boating.%20People%20have%20also%20been%20asked%20to%20keep%20their%20cattle%20away%20from%20the%20river.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20landslides%20blocked%20four%20other%20tunnels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20April%20last%20year%2C%20the%20powerhouse%20protection%20wall%20collapsed%20due%20to%20tail%20race%20channel%20construction%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20the%20project%20site%20has%20been%20hit%20by%20four%20major%20landslides.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20incident%20has%20added%20to%20the%20growing%20concerns%20over%20mega%20dams%20on%20rivers%20in%20the%20eastern%20Himalayan%20belt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20recent%20led%20by%20hydropower%20projects%20in%20the%20eastern%20Himalayas%20ha