Hussain%20has%20offered%20his%20perspective%20on%20the%20debate%2C%20declaring%20Tendulkar%20as%20the%20greatest%20batter%20he%20has%20ever%20witnessed%20or%20faced%20on%20the%20field.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fnews%2Fsachin-tendulkar-vs-virat-kohli-nasser-hussain-weighs-in-on-all-time-great-in-odis-debate%2Farticleshow%2F104797914.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Far%20Has%20Israel%20Succeeded%20In%20Freeing%20Hostages%20Held%20By%20Hamas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHamas%20has%20demanded%20Israel%20to%20release%20all%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20from%20their%20jails%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20hostages%20held%20by%20them%20in%20Gaza.%20Hostages%20have%20very%20high%20political%20currency%20and%20had%20been%20a%20major%20reason%20for%20negotiations%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20October%207%20attack%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20Hamas%20group%20had%20kidnapped%20over%20200%20civilians%20from%20Israeli%20border%20towns%20and%20dragged%20them%20across%20the%20Gazan%20border.%20These%20include%20several%20foreigners%20and%20dual%20citizenship%20holders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20leader%20Yahya%20Sinwar%20recently%20said%20they%20are%20ready%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%26quot%3B%20prisoner%20swap%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20ready%20to%20conduct%20an%20immediate%20prisoner%20exchange%20deal%20that%20includes%20the%20release%20of%20all%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20from%20Israeli%20jails%20in%20exchange%20for%20all%20prisoners%20held%20by%20the%20Palestinian%20resistance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20Israel%20swapped%201%2C027%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20to%20get%20a%20soldier%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20with%20so%20many%20hostages%20held%20by%20Hamas%20in%20a%20war%20zone%2C%20Israel%20faces%20one%20of%20the%20most%20complex%20hostage%20situations%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENegotiations%20seem%20to%20have%20worked%20in%20favour%20of%20Israel%20so%20far%20with%20the%20intervention%20of%20US%20and%20Qatar%2C%20and%20four%20hostages%20have%20been%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHostages%20for%20ceasefire%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20believes%20in%20not%20leaving%20anyone%20behind%2C%20dead%20or%20alive.%20Hamas%20has%20offered%20the%20release%20of%20all%20hostages%20in%20exchange%20of%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20but%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20-%20who%20has%20already%20declared%20a%20war%20against%20Hamas%20-%20may%20not%20give%20any%20reprieve.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESafety%20of%20hostages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20any%20negotiations%20to%20proceed%2C%20Hamas%20will%20have%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20hostages.%20Though%20Hamas%20and%20its%20splinter%20groups%20have%20claimed%20death%20of%20hostages%20in%20aerial%20attacks%20by%20Israel%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20such%20confirmation%20by%20Israel%20or%20any%20other%20country%20who%20have%20their%20citizens%20being%20held%20as%20captive.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20efforts%20to%20free%20the%20hostages%20militarily%20could%20lead%20to%20their%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20will%20hostages%20be%20held%20back%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20may%20agree%20to%20release%20some%20women%2C%20children%20and%20elderly%20people%20in%20order%20to%20retain%20the%20support%20it%20has%20received%20from%20some%20quarters.%20But%20Hamas%20also%20has%20a%20track%20record%20for%20holding%20hostages%20for%20long%20periods%20-%20notably%20Gilad%20Shalit%2C%20the%20Israeli%20soldier%20who%20was%20held%20captive%20for%20five%20years%20before%20being%20eventually%20released%20in%20return%20for%20over%201%2C000%20Palestinian%20prisoners.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698569520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fkuh9r2p8_hamas-hostages-reuters_625x300_25_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-gaza-palestine-how-far-has-israel-succeeded-in-freeing-hostages-held-by-hamas-4524948%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hamas%20has%20demanded%20Israel%20to%20release%20all%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20from%20their%20jails%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20hostages%20held%20by%20them%20in%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-gaza-palestine-how-far-has-israel-succeeded-in-freeing-hostages-held-by-hamas-4524948%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-gaza-palestine-how-far-has-israel-succeeded-in-freeing-hostages-held-by-hamas-4524948%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-gaza-palestine-how-far-has-israel-succeeded-in-freeing-hostages-held-by-hamas-4524948%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Motherhood%20Revisited%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29135734%2FA_view_of_immersion_of_Goddess_Durga_on_the_last_day_of_Durga_Puja_festival_at_Yamuna_River_in_Delhi_on_October_17_2010.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESaakhi%20is%20a%20Sunday%20column%20from%20Mrinal%20Pande%2C%20in%20which%20she%20writes%20about%20what%20she%20sees%20and%20also%20participates%20in.%20That%20has%20been%20her%20burden%20to%20bear%20ever%20since%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20life%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20writer%2C%20editor%2C%20author%2C%20and%20chairperson%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti.%20Her%20journey%20of%20being%20a%20witness-participant%20continues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDurga%20Puja%2C%20celebrated%20in%20the%20autumnal%20month%20of%20Ashwin%2C%20spans%20a%20period%20of%20nine%20days%20for%20worshipping%20the%20nine%20avatars%20of%20Durga.%20Originally%20a%20goddess%20of%20the%20aboriginal%20community%20of%20Shabars%2C%20Durga%20predates%20the%20Vedic%20goddesses%20like%20Aditi%2C%20Ushas%20and%20Aryani.%20In%20many%20respects%20she%20violates%20the%20later%20ideal%20Hindu%20goddess%3A%20submissive%2C%20supportive%20of%20and%20subordinated%20to%20a%20powerful%20male%20deity.%20Her%20images%20worshipped%20during%20the%20Navratri%20or%20Kali%20Pooja%20are%20hardly%20maternal%20in%20the%20traditional%20sense.%20True%2C%20in%20temples%20and%20pandals%20we%20see%20the%20many-armed%20Ma%20with%20her%20children%20Ganesh%2C%20Kartikeya%2C%20Lakshmi%20and%20Saraswati.%20But%20they%20are%20adoptive%2C%20not%20her%20genetic%20children.%20Maternity%20is%20secondary%20to%20her.%20She%20is%20a%20fighter%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3Eyoddha%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20male%20gods%20are%20subservient%20to%20her%20in%20the%20battle%20against%20Mahishasur%2C%20and%20have%20armed%20her%20with%20their%20own%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20327px)%2085vw%2C%20327px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mrinal%20Pande%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22327%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%20525w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%20246w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-642789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22399%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20images%20show%20Durga%20as%20Singhvahini%2C%20astride%20her%20lion%20mount%2C%20thrusting%20a%20trident%20deep%20into%20the%20heart%20of%20demon%20Mahishasur%2C%20who%20is%20half%20male%20and%20half%20water%20buffalo.%20In%20the%20battle%20she%20has%20the%20central%20role%20of%20a%20battle%20queen%20and%20regulator%20of%20cosmos.%20The%20festival%20of%20Dussehra%20that%20falls%20immediately%20after%20on%20the%20tenth%20(lunar)%20day%2C%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20India%20is%20both%20a%20harvest%20festival%20and%20an%20occasion%20to%20celebrate%20Durga%E2%80%99s%20victory%20by%20worshipping%20traditional%20weapons.%20Wine%2C%20meat%20and%20fish%20are%20offered%20to%20the%20deity%20along%20with%20fruits%20and%20Navdhanya%20grown%20in%20clay%20pots%2C%20and%20partaken%20liberally%20as%20her%20%3Cem%3Eprasada%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20especially%20in%20Bengal%20and%20the%20mid%20Himalayan%20region%20and%20bordering%20region%20of%20Nepal%20where%20goats%20and%20buffalos%20are%20still%20sacrificed%20to%20the%20goddess%20and%20Ma%E2%80%99s%20love%20for%20wine%20and%20sacrificial%20meat%20offerings%20is%20unapologetically%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20age%20when%20vegetarianism%20is%20being%20propagated%20as%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20being%20a%20Hindu%2C%20social%20media%20saw%20a%20huge%20row%20erupt.%20Official%20Hindutva%20supporters%20preferred%20the%20taming%20of%20the%20militant%20ten%20armed%20(Dashbhuja%20Ugra)%20Durga%20into%20a%20Mata%20Rani%2C%20the%20queen%20mother%2C%20and%20emphasised%20her%20role%20as%20a%20meek%20daughter%20visiting%20her%20parents%20with%20children.%20The%20cries%20raised%20identified%20her%20as%20the%20obedient%20wife%20of%20Mahadev%20Shiva.%20Like%20any%20married%20daughter%2C%20somewhat%20tired%20of%20the%20austere%20life%20of%20her%20Himalaya-dweller%20husband%2C%20she%20longed%20to%20visit%20her%20parental%20home%20to%20enjoy%20herself.%20So%20there%20was%20an%20overkill%20of%20glamour%20attached%20to%20her%20persona%2C%20dressed%20in%20bright%20red%20and%20gold%20as%20the%20goddess%20of%20harvests%20and%20fertility%3B%20she%20hardly%20appeared%20in%20temples%20at%20least%2C%20as%20a%20military%20general%20commanding%20an%20all%20female%20army.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20noticeable%20change%20was%20a%20stamping%20of%20non-vegetarian%20food%20offerings%20as%20non-sacred%20on%20social%20media.%20The%20tribe%20of%20neo-Sanatanis%20frowns%20heavily%20on%20non-vegetarianism%20and%20many%20housing%20societies%20they%20control%20not%20just%20refuse%20to%20have%20tenants%20who%20eat%20meat%20but%20keep%20a%20regular%20check%20on%20their%20kitchens%20and%20take%20out%20orders%20brought%20into%20the%20%E2%80%9Csanctified%E2%80%9D%20buildings.%20Both%20changes%20underscored%20the%20denial%20of%20personal%20choices%20ordinary%20women%20have%20long%20suffered%2C%20first%20as%20women%20and%20then%20as%20mothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20overall%20downgrading%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20persona%20as%20weak%2C%20non%20combative%2C%20menstrual%20blood%20contaminating%2C%20one%20has%20often%20wondered%20why%20are%20we%20alive%20at%20all%3F%20The%20fact%20is%2C%20without%20women%20there%20can%20be%20no%20%C2%A0human%20life%20on%20our%20planet.%20Also%20young%20human%20males%20too%20depend%20upon%20nurture%20longer%20than%20any%20other%20mammal%20species.%20So%20patriarchy%20after%20it%20had%20replaced%20goddesses%20Vac%2C%20Ushas%20and%20Diti%20with%20the%20male%20triad%20of%20Brahma%2C%20Vishnu%20and%20Mahesh%2C%20a%20new%20division%20of%20labour%20was%20established.%20It%20was%20mandated%20that%20women%E2%80%99s%20central%20role%20will%20be%20maternal.%20They%20shall%20not%20only%20bear%20and%20nurture%20children%20but%20will%20be%20totally%20responsible%20for%20them%20in%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20first%20decade%20of%20their%20lives%2C%20while%20men%20control%20the%20outside%20world%20and%20create%20empires.%20As%20physical%20and%20psychic%20rites%20of%20passage%20go%20under%20this%20law%2C%20%E2%80%98to%20father%20a%20child%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20male%20context%20largely%20means%20providing%20a%20sperm%2C%20and%20at%20the%20most%20providing%20a%20steady%20income%20to%20sustain%20the%20child%20that%20is%20born%20thereafter.%20Women%E2%80%99s%20status%20as%20child%20bearers%20and%20nurturers%20demanded%20their%20continuous%20presence%20for%20years%2C%20feeding%2C%20cleaning%2C%20cooking%2C%20punishing%2C%20rewarding%2C%20marking%20special%20occasions%20and%20chaperoning%20the%20child%20(mostly%20alone)%20for%20a%20timespan%20that%20dominated%20their%20entire%20youthful%2C%20productive%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20daughter%20I%20was%20witness%20to%20my%20gifted%20mother%20always%20putting%20herself%20last%2C%20writing%20whenever%20she%20could%20squeeze%20out%20a%20few%20hours%20under%20a%20pseudonym%20of%20Shivani%2C%20using%20the%20cheapest%20paper%2C%20keeping%20her%20head%20down%20to%20stay%20off%20the%20radar%20of%20the%20family%20and%20still%20being%20taunted%20for%20not%20being%20good%20enough%20as%20a%20mother.%20And%20as%20she%20gained%20popularity%2C%20being%20pushed%20aside%20by%20male%20critics%20as%20writing%20on%20domestic%20themes%20and%20women%20and%20children.%20The%20term%20%E2%80%98domestic%E2%80%99%20was%20never%20used%20pejoratively%20for%20male%20writers%20churning%20out%20reams%20of%20writing%20about%20families%2C%20especially%20their%20mothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20where%20we%20stand%20now%2C%20that%20template%20for%20motherhood%20was%20a%20keystone%20of%20a%20most%20diverse%20socio-political%20system%20that%20first%20segregated%20and%20then%20kept%20mothers%20at%20home%2C%20passive%20and%20modest%20and%20patient%2C%20or%20else%20they%20risked%20being%20labeled%20as%20slutty%20mums%20like%20the%20mother%20in%20Mannoo%20Bhandari%E2%80%99s%20classic%20%3Cem%3EAapka%20Bunty%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Amazingly%20as%20Durga%20worshippers%2C%20even%20the%20believers%20in%20the%20Shakta%20tradition%20in%20the%20hill%20regions%20harboured%20several%20unexamined%20assumptions%3A%20one%2C%20a%20mother%20is%20a%20mother%20is%20a%20mother.%20She%20shall%20find%20her%20chief%20gratification%20through%20mothering.%20Durga%20loomed%20large%20before%20them%20but%20as%20priests%20and%20controllers%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20coffers%20and%20armies%2C%20they%20asked%20Mother%20Durga%20to%20lend%20them%20back%20their%20arms%3A%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Ma%20Durge!%20Give%20us%20victory%20(%3Cem%3EJayam%20Dehi%3C%2Fem%3E).%E2%80%99%20Never%20mind%20if%20it%20disempowered%20their%20own%20women%20and%20overlooked%20how%20Durga%E2%80%99s%20own%20deemed%20motherhood%20never%20deterred%20her%20from%20going%20into%20the%20battle%20field%20and%20winning.%20Another%20myth%20the%20neo-Hindutva%20supporters%20have%20clung%20to%20is%20that%20a%20mother%20loves%20her%20sons%20unconditionally%20no%20matter%20how%20the%20sons%20treat%20her.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EKuputro%20jayet%20kwachidapi%20kumata%20na%20bhavati%3C%2Fem%3E%20(S%20son%20may%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20bad%20but%20never%20the%20mother%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Adi%20Shankaracharya.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20Madonisation%20of%20the%20mother%20puts%20exceptional%20demands%20on%20harassed%2C%20perpetually%20overworked%20(and%20often%20short%20of%20cash)%20mothers%20while%20downgrading%20their%20potential%20as%20workers%20and%20leaders%20of%20men.%20Ask%20flesh%20and%20blood%20mothers.%20While%20the%20innocence%20and%20beauty%20of%20a%20child%20melts%20one%E2%80%99s%20heart%2C%20children%E2%80%99s%20need%20for%20constant%20attention%2C%20patience%20and%20expectation%20of%20an%20endless%20jollity%20from%20mothers%20often%20drives%20isolated%20young%20mothers%20into%20a%20deep%20despair.%20After%20Covid%2C%20there%20is%20a%20reported%20rise%20in%20the%20infamous%20post-natal%20blues%20that%20now%20seem%20to%20last%20years%2C%20not%20days.%20And%20we%20continue%20to%20believe%20motherhood%20is%20its%20own%20reward!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWomen%20in%20my%20generation%20became%20mothers%20in%20the%20late%2060s%20in%20an%20India%20steadily%20moving%20towards%20nuclear%20families%20and%20consumerism.%20Still%20husbands%2C%20in-laws%20and%20parents%20awaited%20the%20birth%20of%20the%20first%20grandchild%2C%20preferably%20a%20male%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20knot%20was%20tied.%20To%20be%20a%20mother%20was%20becoming%20a%20complete%20woman.%20This%20posed%20problems%20for%20those%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98complete%20like%20other%20women%E2%80%99%20but%20had%20complex%20dreams%20about%20a%20career%20much%20like%20their%20husbands%E2%80%99%20that%20would%20make%20them%20feel%20fulfilled%20and%20proud%20of%20themselves.%20The%20problem%20was%20the%20prevalent%20view%20of%20parenthood%20still%20presupposed%20the%20husband%E2%80%99s%20career%20to%20be%20more%20important%20for%20the%20family%20than%20the%20wife%E2%80%99s.%20Offers%20of%20help%20from%20men%20were%20construed%20as%20acts%20of%20generosity%2C%20not%20a%20justified%20duty.%20Intellectually%2C%20we%20knew%20the%20injustice%20in%20homes%20and%20workplaces%2C%20but%20the%20emotion-laden%20heavy%20maternal%20duties%20which%20we%2C%20the%20worshippers%20of%20Ma%20Durga%2C%20were%20handed%2C%20created%20within%20our%20minds%20a%20clutter%20and%20perennially%20short%20for%20time%2C%20we%20erred%20on%20the%20side%20of%20peace%20and%20functioned%20as%20a%20single%20parent%20while%20working%20full%20time.%20Still%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20family%2C%20the%20fathers%20%E2%80%9Cworked%E2%80%9D.%20We%20the%20working%20mothers%2C%20struggling%20to%20bring%20our%20lives%20in%20focus%20after%20a%20professional%20gap%20of%20four-five%20years%2C%20were%20believed%20to%20be%20denying%20our%20children%E2%80%99s%20authentic%20needs%20in%20direct%20proportion%20to%20our%20visibility%20as%20good%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEvery%20Navratri%2C%20Durga%20thrusting%20her%20spear%20into%20the%20heart%20of%20darkness%20reminds%20us%20that%20motherhood%20has%20a%20history%2C%20an%20ideology%20that%20is%20more%20fundamental%20than%20nationalism%20or%20any%20political%20%E2%80%98isms%E2%80%99.%20In%20this%20tribal%20goddess%2C%20two%20ideas%20merge%3A%20the%20female%20body%20as%20males%20have%20defined%20it%20is%20a%20lie.%20The%20goddess%20will%20drink%2C%20eat%20meat%2C%20play%20football%20with%20demons%E2%80%99%20heads%2C%20but%20remain%20beneficent%2C%20pure%20and%20is%20the%20only%20source%20of%20recreating%20life%20and%20sustaining%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMrinal%20Pande%20is%20a%20writer%20and%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698568809000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29135734%2FA_view_of_immersion_of_Goddess_Durga_on_the_last_day_of_Durga_Puja_festival_at_Yamuna_River_in_Delhi_on_October_17_2010.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmotherhood-revisited%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Every%20Navratri%2C%20Durga%20thrusting%20her%20spear%20into%20the%20heart%20of%20darkness%20reminds%20us%20that%20motherhood%20has%20a%20history%2C%20an%20ideology%20that%20is%20more%20fundamental%20than%20nationalism%20or%20any%20political%20'isms'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmotherhood-revisited%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%20On%20High%20Alert%20After%20Serial%20Blasts%20In%20Kerala%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkerala-news%2Fkerala-blast-jehovah-witness-prayer-meet-series-of-blasts-at-prayer-meet-in-kerala-killed-injured-4524571%5C%22%3Eserial%20blasts%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20a%20prayer%20meeting%20of%20Jehovah's%20Witnesses%20at%20a%20convention%20centre%20in%20Kerala's%20Kalamassery%20today%2C%20security%20has%20been%20tightened%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20and%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20said%20that%20security%20has%20been%20stepped%20up%20in%20crowded%20areas%20of%20the%20city%20in%20view%20of%20the%20blasts.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%20has%20issued%20a%20high%20alert%20and%20increased%20security%20in%20view%20of%20the%20festive%20season%2C%20upcoming%20c