img%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104797009.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EActor%20Lee%20Sun%20Kyun%20is%20being%20probed%20in%20a%20drug%20scandal.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20he%20appeared%20at%20the%20police%20station%20for%20an%20interrogation%20session.%20He%20cooperated%20with%20authorities%20by%20submitting%20his%20phone%20for%20investigation%20and%20underwent%20drug%20tests%2C%20which%20returned%20negative%20results.%20However%2C%20the%20police%20stated%20that%20these%20tests%20may%20not%20be%20entirely%20conclusive%20due%20to%20the%20passage%20of%20time.%20Lee%20Sun%20Kyun%20also%20apologized%20for%20the%20disappointment%20he%20caused%20and%20expressed%20his%20commitment%20to%20the%20investigation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gujarat%20Man%20Pretending%20to%20Be%20a%20Govt%20Officer%20Amasses%20Funds%20Worth%20Over%20Rs%204%20Crore%2C%20Arrested%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20144110%2Fajin-k-s-bOoEVNhRX_k-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0Gujarat%20Police%20has%20arrested%20an%20executive%20engineer%2C%20albeit%20a%20fake%20one%2C%20who%20flaunted%20his%20government%20credentials%20and%20embezzled%20roughly%20Rs%204.15%20crore%20for%20%E2%80%9Ctribal%20welfare%E2%80%9D.%20He%20gathered%20the%20money%20for%20more%20than%2093%20tribal%20welfare%20schemes.%20He%20had%20also%20opened%20up%20his%20government%20office%20in%20Chhota%20Udepur%20district%20of%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20Kiran%20Patel%20and%20Mayank%20Tiwari%20have%20been%20caught%20claiming%20to%20be%20top%20men%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20(PMO).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Sandip%20Rajput%20confidently%20introduced%20himself%20as%20an%20executive%20engineer%20and%20claimed%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20Gujarat%20government%E2%80%99s%20irrigation%20department.%20He%20set%20up%20his%20base%20in%20Bodeli%2C%20in%20Chhota%20Udepur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20set%20up%20a%20fake%20office%20too%20on%20July%2021%2C%202021%2C%20and%20put%20a%20nameplate%20that%20described%20him%20%E2%80%98Executive%20Engineer%2C%20Irrigation%20Project%20Division%2C%20Bodeli%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajput%20also%20forged%20documents%2C%20signatures%20and%20other%20documents%20to%20portray%20himself%20as%20a%20government%20official.%20He%20acquired%2093%20government%20projects%20and%20received%20funds%20accumulating%20over%20Rs%204.15%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20complaint%20was%20registered%20by%20Javed%20Maknojiya%2C%20working%20as%20a%20junior%20clerk%20in%20the%20administrative%20office%20of%20the%20district%20collectorate.%20As%20per%20the%20FIR%2C%20the%20matter%20came%20to%20light%20when%20district%20collector%20(DC)%20Sachin%20Kumar%20convened%20a%20meeting%20on%20October%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20meeting%2C%20applications%20requesting%20for%20Rs%203.78%20crores%20for%2012%20border%20village%20and%20lift%20irrigation%20projects%20were%20discussed%2C%20when%20officials%20realised%20that%20no%20office%20of%20the%20executive%20engineer%20existed%20in%20Bodeli.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20investigation%20was%20launched%2C%20the%20DC%20sought%20details%20of%20the%20projects%20run%20by%20the%20Bodeli%20%E2%80%98office%E2%80%99%20and%20found%20that%20Rajput%20had%20received%20Rs%204.15%20crores%20since%202021%2C%20after%20which%20he%20and%20his%20associate%20Abu%20Bakr%20Saiyed%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Gujarat%20has%20witnessed%20several%20fraud%20cases%20where%20the%20accused%20impersonate%20government%20officials%20including%20those%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20(CMO).%20One%20of%20these%20cases%20involved%20conman%20Kiran%20Patel%2C%20who%20claimed%20to%20be%20a%20top%20director%20handling%20strategies%20and%20campaigns%20in%20the%20PMO.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPatel%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Ahmedabad%20City%20Detection%20of%20Crime%20Branch%20(DCB)%20in%20April%20after%20the%20Gujarat%20Police%20took%20his%20custody%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20The%20police%20arrested%20many%20others%20including%20Viraj%20Patel%2C%20Nikunj%20Patel%20and%20Lavkush%20Patel%2C%20who%20claimed%20to%20be%20officials%20of%20the%20CMO.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vibesofindia.com%2Ffake-feast-on-in-gujarat-yet-another-sarkari-fake-caught%2F%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vibesofindia.com%2F%5C%22%3EVibes%20of%20India.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698566927000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20144110%2Fajin-k-s-bOoEVNhRX_k-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgujarat-man-pretending-to-be-a-govt-officer-amasses-funds-worth-over-rs-4-crore-arrested%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Gujarat%20has%20witnessed%20several%20fraud%20cases%20where%20the%20accused%20impersonate%20government%20officials%20including%20those%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgujarat-man-pretending-to-be-a-govt-officer-amasses-funds-worth-over-rs-4-crore-arrested%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20What%20Is%20Sim%20Swapping%20Scam%3F%20How%20To%20Protect%20Yourself%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20Delhi%20advocate%20has%20claimed%20that%20she%20lost%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Csim%20swapping%20scam%26quot%3B.%20As%20per%20an%20Indian%20Express%20report%2C%20the%20woman%20received%20three%20missed%20calls%20from%20an%20unknown%20number.%20After%20she%20called%20back%20from%20a%20different%20number%2C%20the%20person%20said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20courier%20call.%20The%20woman%20then%20shared%20her%20house%20address%2C%20the%20report%20added.%20After%20sharing%20the%20details%2C%20the%2035-year-old%20reportedly%20got%20two%20transaction%20notifications%20from%20her%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDelhi%20Police's%20cyber%20unit%20said%20the%20woman%20didn't%20share%20any%20information%20like%20OTP%20(one%20time%20password)%20with%20the%20scammer.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20Sim%20Swapping%20Scam%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20scammer%20manages%20to%20get%20access%20to%20your%20SIM%20card.%20They%20trick%20the%20network%20provider%20into%20linking%20your%20number%20to%20the%20SIM%20card%20they%20have%20in%20possession.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20protect%20yourself%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20basic%20points%20that%20one%20should%20keep%20in%20mind%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Never%20entertain%20a%20person%20who%20sounds%20suspicious%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20If%20your%20sim%20card%20is%20locked%20or%20it%20shows%20an%20error%20message%20like%20%E2%80%9Cno%20valid%2C%E2%80%9D%20immediately%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20your%20service%20provider%20and%20block%20your%20number.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20You%20can%20also%20avail%20of%20the%20sim%20lock%20facility.%20It%20will%20help%20keep%20your%20details%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%93%20Following%20this%2C%20block%20your%20UPI%20and%20internet%20banking.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Keep%20changing%20your%20passwords%20at%20regular%20intervals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Keep%20a%20check%20on%20your%20account%20details.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20In%20case%20of%20any%20fraudulent%20transaction%2C%20you%20must%20inform%20the%20bank%20immediately.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20You%20can%20opt%20for%20a%20two-factor%20authentication%20security%20feature.%20It%20will%20help%20keep%20your%20details%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20does%20it%20take%20to%20crack%20passwords%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERecently%2C%20Paytm%20founder%20and%20CEO%20Vijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma%20spoke%20about%20how%20much%20time%20a%20hacker%20takes%20to%20crack%20passwords.%20He%20also%20spoke%C2%A0about%20the%20importance%20of%20passwords.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharma%20said%20that%20it%20is%20the%20length%20of%20the%20password%20that%20matters%20the%20most.%20He%20has%20shared%20a%20detailed%20chart%20on%20X%20-%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter.%20The%20note%20attached%20to%20it%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20length%20of%20the%20password%20that%20matters%20most.%20Add%20a%20few%20small%20caps%20to%20make%20one.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIt%20is%20length%20of%20password%20that%20matters%20most.%20Add%20few%20small%20caps%20alphabets%20too%20to%20make%20one.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FCATY4gSEPk%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FCATY4gSEPk%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Vijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma%20(%40vijayshekhar)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fvijayshekhar%2Fstatus%2F1713068431157993846%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EFor%20number-only%20passwords%2C%20the%20time%20taken%20by%20a%20hacker%20can%20vary%20from%20%E2%80%9Cinstantly%20to%20six%20days%E2%80%9D%20depending%20on%20its%20characters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698566700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fad85e4r_mobile-phone-generic_62