%2FDr-Michelle-4-1698418132-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDr-Michelle-4-1698418132-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333190%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShishur%20Sevay%20is%20home%20to%2014%20girls%20who%20are%20enrolled%20in%20various%20vocational%20courses.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20device%20is%20designed%20for%20people%20with%20conditions%20such%20as%20cerebral%20palsy%2C%20ALS%2C%20Rett%20syndrome%2C%20aphasia%20or%20spinal%20cord%20injury%20to%20gain%20access%20to%20computers%2C%20to%20communicate%2C%20and%20to%20control%20their%20home%20environment%20with%20just%20their%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20home%20is%20meant%20for%20permanence%2C%20for%20long%20term%20security%2C%20to%20be%20a%20safe%20place%20for%20those%20who%20may%20eventually%20leave%2C%20and%20a%20permanent%20home%20for%20those%20who%20require%20full-time%20care%20due%20to%20their%20disabilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20home%20is%20inclusive%2C%20meaning%20there%20are%20no%20separate%20units%20based%20on%20abilities.%20Their%20lives%20matter%20and%20we%20intend%20to%20be%20a%20model%20of%20what%20can%20be%20done.%20Inclusion%20made%20us%20a%20home%2C%20a%20family%2C%20not%20an%20institution%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%2015%20years%2C%20Dr%20Michelle%20has%20faced%20several%20challenges.%20Initially%2C%20she%20had%20to%20fight%20the%20local%20men%20who%20wanted%20a%20key%20to%20the%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20saw%20it%20as%20a%20public%20property%20and%20were%20especially%20angry%20that%20a%20foreigner%20lived%20here.%20There%20were%20rumours%20that%20I%20was%20raising%20the%20girls%20in%20order%20to%20sell%20them%20for%20a%20higher%20price%20abroad.%20I%20was%20given%20death%20threats%20as%20I%20refused%20to%20hire%20people%