Science%20DIY%20kits.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20is%20to%20foster%20curiosity%2C%20innovation%20and%20critical%20thinking%20skills%20among%20students%20from%20classes%206%20to%2010%2C%20adds%20Abhishek.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAshutosh%20Pandit%2C%20founder%20of%20STEM%20Learning%2C%20says%20that%20they%20want%20students%20in%20government%20schools%20to%20have%20access%20to%20the%20same%20resources%20as%20private%20school%20students%20so%20that%20they%20too%20can%20excel%20in%20these%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20at%20a%20grassroots%20level%20to%20enable%20students%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20science.%20Many%20have%20a%20phobia%20of%20science%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20conceptual%20clarity.%20So%20we%20enable%20teachers%20to%20connect%20with%20students%20better%20through%20our%20teaching%20aids.%20We%20help%20them%20learn%20through%20experiments.%20Our%20science%20labs%20are%20innovative%20and%20interactive%20with%20a%20hands-on%20approach%20to%20facilitate%20the%20learning%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330978%2Fkamlesh-atwal-started-nanakmatta-public-school-uttarakhand-holistic-education-for-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESTEM%20learning%3C%2Fa%3E%20sets%20up%20mini%20science%20centres%2C%20which%20consist%20of%2080%20plug-and-play%20science%20and%20maths%20models.%20Students%20can%20understand%20the%20concepts%20through%20observation.%20They%20also%20set%20up%20tinkering%20labs%2C%20which%20help%20them%20develop%20skills%20and%20build%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20teachers%20explaining%20concepts%20on%20the%20blackboard%2C%20learning%20through%20practical%20experiments%20helps%20students%20learn%20better.%20Science%20should%20not%20be%20taught%20on%20a%20rote%20basis%2C%20it%20should%20be%20hands-on%20teaching%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Ashutosh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D