-8-min-1697205338.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-8-min-1697205338-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-8-min-1697205338-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-8-min-1697205338-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-8-min-1697205338-1536x1023.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-8-min-1697205338-150x100.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-8-min-1697205338-272x182.jpeg%20272w%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20banker%20Vidyasagar%20Hariharan%20caught%20his%20first%20glimpse%20of%20the%20flamingos%20that%20visited%20Mumbai%20in%202016%2C%20he%20fell%20in%20love.%20He%20recalls%20the%20moment%20as%20%E2%80%9Cmagical%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20heard%20a%20loud%20noise%20as%20we%20were%20nearing%20the%20waterbody.%20It%20was%20the%20sound%20of%20thousands%20of%20flamingos%20cackling.%20The%20rising%20sun%20painted%20the%20murky%20tidal%20waters%20and%20the%20pink%20birds%20golden.%20I%20was%20enamoured%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2047-year-old.%20Since%20that%20day%2C%20Vidyasagar%20has%20made%20a%20visit%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332196%2Fvidyasagar-hariharan-flamingos-mumbai-thane-creek-conserve-wetlands-wildlife-photography%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20wetlands%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20part%20of%20his%20routine%2C%20while%20also%20extensively%20researching%20the%20birds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20a%20peek%20into%20his%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Waswo%20X%20Waswo%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20size