what%20their%20children%20had%20been%20doing%20during%20the%20camp.%20A%20two-hour%20performance%20by%20the%20students%20would%20be%20followed%20with%20tea%20and%20snacks%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20did%20an%20MS%20patient%20manage%20to%20do%20all%20this%3F%20Ask%20her%20and%20Sudha%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20you%20need%20is%20courage%20and%20support%20from%20the%20family.%E2%80%9D%20She%20is%20immensely%20grateful%20to%20her%20husband%20who%20took%20such%20good%20care%20of%20her%20down%20the%20years%2C%20without%20a%20single%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESudha%20lost%20her%20husband%20to%20cancer%20a%20decade%20ago.%C2%A0%20The%20couple%20has%20no%20children.%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20all%20that%20she%20has%20gone%20through%2C%20she%20has%20a%20ready%20smile%20for%20everyone%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jayashree.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMamtha%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CShe%20taught%20us%20to%20delegate%20work%20and%20encouraged%20us%20to%20think%20of%20it%20as%20%E2%80%98our%20camp%E2%80%99.%20We%20all%20learnt%20a%20lot%20from%20this%20endeavour%20of%20hers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20after%20almost%20three%20decades%2C%20some%20of%20the%20students%20share%20their%20fond%20memories%20of%20the%20summer%20camps.%20Manasa%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlways%20calm%20and%20composed%20with%20a%20smiling%20face%2C%20Sudha%20ma%E2%80%99am%20was%20the%20calm%20within%20the%20storm%20of%20kids%20at%20Siddhi%20Creations.%20She%20embodies%20Maria%20Montessori%E2%80%99s%20(an%20Italian%20educator)%20words%2C%20%E2%80%98follow%20the%20child%E2%80%99.%20She%20gave%20us%20the%20freedom%20to%20create%20and%20thrive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajath%2C%20who%20is%20an%20advocate%20today%2C%20notes%20how%20%E2%80%9CSudha%20aunty%20showered%20the%20same%20love%20on%20all%20of%20us%20and%20took%20care%20of%20all%20details%2C%20giving%20us%20the%20lesson%20of%20what%20true%20leadership%20was.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20Vijetha%2C%20who%20works%20as%20an%20H